<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Confirmação de Cadastro</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fredoka&display=swap');

        /* Estilos para mobile-first */
        @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                width: 100% !important;
                padding: 10px !important;
            }

            .button {
                padding: 14px 20px !important;
                font-size: 16px !important;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 22px !important;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 16px !important;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body
    style="margin:0; padding:0; font-family: 'Fredoka', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #1d2d69; color: #1d2d69;">
    <table role="presentation" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
        <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding: 20px 0;">
                <table class="container" role="presentation" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="600"
                    style="width: 600px; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;">
                    <tr>
                        <td align="center" bgcolor="#f9b233" style="padding: 20px;">
                            <h2
                                style="margin: 0; color: #1d2d69; font-family: 'Fredoka', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 26px;">
                                Bem-vindo ao Estrela Dalva!</h2>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td
                            style="padding: 30px 40px; text-align: left; color: #1d2d69; font-family: 'Fredoka', Arial, sans-serif;">
                            <p style="font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 20px;">Olá, {{nomeCliente}}</p>
                            <p style="font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 20px;">
                                Obrigado por se cadastrar! Confirme seu e-mail para começar a aproveitar todas as
                                as funcionalidades do sistema do parque.
                            </p>
                            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 40px 0;">
                                <a href="{{{urlConfirmacao}}}"
                                    style="background-color: #00c2c7; color: #ffffff; padding: 16px 32px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 18px; display: inline-block; font-family: 'Fredoka', Arial, sans-serif;"
                                    class="button">
                                    Confirmar Cadastro
                                </a>
                            </div>
                            <p style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0;">
                                Estamos ansiosos para te receber!
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td align="center" bgcolor="#f04e23"
                            style="padding: 15px; color: #ffffff; font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Fredoka', Arial, sans-serif;">
                            © 2025 Parque Aquático Estrela Dalva
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>

</html>